Name: proc read_chan {cmd filename args} {set ch [open $filename rb];fconfigure $ch -translation binary;set bsize [fconfigure $ch -buffersize];set new [$cmd {*}$args -chan $ch];while {![eof $new]} {set result [read $new $bsize]};close $new;return $result}
proc accumulate {string args} {set cmd [{*}$args -command dcmd];$cmd update [string range $string 0 20];$cmd update [string range $string 21 end];return [$cmd finalize]}
